Polokwane Municipality has issued a weather warning about thunderstorms observed about 20 km south of the city and towards Lebowakgomo. Meanwhile footage received shows visuals of a hail storm between Mokopane and Mookgophong along the N1 South earlier this afternoon (Thursday).
Matshidiso Mothapo on behalf of Polokwane Municipality alerted ratepayers of the city by text message on heavy downpours that might result in localised flooding.
He advised residents to stay indoors under such conditions.